<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.2">
<l>oṉṟu maṟivoṉṟil lāta vuruvaṟaik kōpālar taṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kaṉṟukāl māṟumā pōlē kaṉṉiyirun tāḷaik koṇṭu</l>
<l>naṉṟum kiṟiceytu pōṉāṉ nārāyaṇaṉ ceyta tīmai</l>
<l>eṉṟu memarkaḷ kuṭikkō rēccuk kolāyiṭuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mischief perpetrated by Nārāyaṇaṉ who,</l>
<l rend="indent">like an unattractive herder</l>
<l rend="indent">without knowledge of anything at all,</l>
<l>comes along with clever trickery [and] takes her, [our] virgin girl,</l>
<l rend="indent">as if stealing a calf</l>
<l>has become a constant affliction of abuse to our clan, has it not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
